    "The applications of generative AI span various industries, including art, writing, software development, healthcare, finance, gaming, marketing, and fashion.",
    "The early 2020s witnessed a surge in investment in generative AI by major companies like Microsoft, Google, and Baidu, as well as numerous smaller firms.",
